text: Matthew "Maddog" Moore is a former National Basketball League basketballer from Townsville Queensland, who won a NBL Championship with South East Melbourne Magic in 1996 and played in the 1997 NBL Final Series.http://www.members.optusnet.com.au/~mshoops/champions_2.html He also played for Brisbane Bullets and Newcastle Falcons. Moore is the brother of former rugby league state of Origin and Test player Danny Moore. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1972 births
title: Matt Moore (basketball)
